title: I Challenged A Psychic vs. A Stock Broker
description: In this video, Max Fosh challenges a psychic and a stock broker to predict the future. He tests their abilities by asking them to predict the outcome of various events.
summary: Max Fosh pits a psychic against a stock broker in a competition to predict the future.
payoff: The payoff comes when the psychic and stock broker struggle to accurately predict the future events, showcasing the unpredictability of life and the limitations of their respective professions.
